  <div class="grid__item three-fifths lap-two-thirds palm-one-whole">
    <p>If you select the <q>Image Server</q> link for the register (not the <q>Access Image Server Directly</q> button) you will get a screen of basic information about the Source of these Images — it will be blank for a new Source.</p>
    <p>Select <q>Edit Image Source</q> and enter the information about this specific source including the start and end dates. If this is a new Register but there are already other Registers with the same information (except dates), you can go to one of those Registers and propagate (cascade) the information to this new one.</p>
  </div>

