      <img src="/system/images/W1siZiIsIjIwMTkvMDcvMTcvNm4xc2RzMWc0Ml91cGxvYWRfcHJvZ3Jlc3MucG5nIl1d/upload-progress.png?sha=fe1438170df57770" title="Upload progress" alt="Upload progress" data-rel="225x255" width="1600" height="885" />
      <figcaption>Fig. 10 — upload progress</figcaption>
    </figure>
  </div>
  <div class="grid__item three-fifths lap-two-thirds palm-one-whole">
    <p>On completion you will return to the page from which you requested the upload which will contain a list of images that were uploaded.</p>
  </div>

