  <div class="grid__item three-fifths lap-two-thirds palm-one-whole">
    <p>If you select a specific <q>Show Images</q> button, you will see a listing of all Images that are there. You can view and or download a specific image.</p>

    <p>Please note that if your browser can’t display the image file, it will simply download it for you.</p>
